DDD Documentation					-*- text -*-
*****************

This directory contains various documentation related to DDD in
PostScript format.

ddd.man.ps -- The DDD manual page


The following documents may also be of interest to DDD users:

ddd-thesis.ps -- ``DDD - ein Debugger mit graphischer Datendarstellung''

    Dorothea's Master's Thesis on DDD (in German).


gdb.ps -- ``Debugging with GDB''

    The GDB manual.


vse.ps -- ``Visual Prettyprinting''

    This paper decribes the VSL language, which DDD uses to display data
    structures in displays.  Contains a short VSL reference.


These documents are available via anonymous FTP in 
<ftp://ftp.ips.tu.bs.de/pub/local/softech/ddd/doc/>,

